static gunichar
string_get_char (const gchar* self,
                 glong index)
{

}

BalaGIdlParser*
bala_gidl_parser_construct (GType object_type)
{
	BalaGIdlParser* self = NULL;
	self = (BalaGIdlParser*) bala_code_visitor_construct (object_type);
	return self;
}

BalaGIdlParser*
bala_gidl_parser_new (void)
{
	return bala_gidl_parser_construct (BALA_TYPE_GIDL_PARSER);
}

static void
bala_gidl_parser_class_init (BalaGIdlParserClass * klass,
                             gpointer klass_data)
{
	bala_gidl_parser_parent_class = g_type_class_peek_parent (klass);
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->finalize = bala_gidl_parser_finalize;
	g_type_class_adjust_private_offset (klass, &BalaGIdlParser_private_offset);
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_namespace = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaNamespace*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_namespace;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_class = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaClass*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_class;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_struct = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaStruct*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_struct;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_interface = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaInterface*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_interface;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_enum = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaEnum*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_enum;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_error_domain = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaErrorDomain*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_error_domain;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_delegate = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaDelegate*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_delegate;
	((BalaCodeVisitorClass *) klass)->visit_source_file = (void (*) (BalaCodeVisitor*, BalaSourceFile*)) bala_gidl_parser_real_visit_source_file;
}

static void
bala_gidl_parser_instance_init (BalaGIdlParser * self,
                                gpointer klass)
{
	self->priv = bala_gidl_parser_get_instance_private (self);
}

static void
bala_gidl_parser_finalize (BalaCodeVisitor * obj)
{
	BalaGIdlParser * self;
	self = G_TYPE_CHECK_INSTANCE_CAST (obj, BALA_TYPE_GIDL_PARSER, BalaGIdlParser);
	_bala_code_context_unref0 (self->priv->context);
	_bala_source_file_unref0 (self->priv->current_source_file);
	_bala_source_reference_unref0 (self->priv->current_source_reference);
	_bala_code_node_unref0 (self->priv->current_namespace);
	_bala_code_node_unref0 (self->priv->current_data_type);
	_bala_map_unref0 (self->priv->codenode_attributes_map);
	_bala_map_unref0 (self->priv->codenode_attributes_patterns);
	_bala_iterable_unref0 (self->priv->current_type_symbol_set);
	_bala_map_unref0 (self->priv->cname_type_map);
	BALA_CODE_VISITOR_CLASS (bala_gidl_parser_parent_class)->finalize (obj);
}

/**
 * Code visitor parsing all GIDL files.
 */
static GType
bala_gidl_parser_get_type_once (void)
{
	static const GTypeInfo g_define_type_info = { sizeof (BalaGIdlParserClass), (GBaseInitFunc) NULL, (GBaseFinalizeFunc) NULL, (GClassInitFunc) bala_gidl_parser_class_init, (GClassFinalizeFunc) NULL, NULL, sizeof (BalaGIdlParser), 0, (GInstanceInitFunc) bala_gidl_parser_instance_init, NULL };
	GType bala_gidl_parser_type_id;
	bala_gidl_parser_type_id = g_type_register_static (BALA_TYPE_CODE_VISITOR, "BalaGIdlParser", &g_define_type_info, 0);
	BalaGIdlParser_private_offset = g_type_add_instance_private (bala_gidl_parser_type_id, sizeof (BalaGIdlParserPrivate));
	return bala_gidl_parser_type_id;
}

GType
bala_gidl_parser_get_type (void)
{
	static volatile gsize bala_gidl_parser_type_id__volatile = 0;
	if (g_once_init_enter (&bala_gidl_parser_type_id__volatile)) {
		GType bala_gidl_parser_type_id;
		bala_gidl_parser_type_id = bala_gidl_parser_get_type_once ();
		g_once_init_leave (&bala_gidl_parser_type_id__volatile, bala_gidl_parser_type_id);
	}
	return bala_gidl_parser_type_id__volatile;
}

static void
_bala_array_destroy (gpointer array,
                     gint array_length,
                     GDestroyNotify destroy_func)
{
	if ((array != NULL) && (destroy_func != NULL)) {
		gint i;
		for (i = 0; i < array_length; i = i + 1) {
			if (((gpointer*) array)[i] != NULL) {
				destroy_func (((gpointer*) array)[i]);
			}
		}
	}
}

static void
_bala_array_free (gpointer array,
                  gint array_length,
                  GDestroyNotify destroy_func)
{
	_bala_array_destroy (array, array_length, destroy_func);
	g_free (array);
}

static gint
_bala_array_length (gpointer array)
{
	gint length;
	length = 0;
	if (array) {
		while (((gpointer*) array)[length]) {
			length++;
		}
	}
	return length;
}
